{"id": 2655, "title": "Ticket #2655: Bugs in gridmanager's handling of x509 email attribute", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe gridmanager's handling of the email attribute of x509 proxies (added in <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1934\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1934'); return false;\" title=\"Job ClassAd should persist the x509 email\">#1934</a></span>) has a couple bugs. These can result in memory leaks, uninitialized pointers that can cause a crash, and the x509UserProxyEmail attribute not being set for jobs forwarded via Condor-C.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Nov-22 17:03</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/35158464368f538e693badf3c87ab495417c50cb\">[28412]</a></span>: Fix typo in version history. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2655\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2655'); return false;\" title=\"Bugs in gridmanager's handling of x509 email attribute\">#2655</a></span> ===VersionHistory:Complete===  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Nov-22 16:42</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/603f56cf119ea9d1e2a8f21b0e96af9529382ba1\">[28411]</a></span>: Fix bad handling of x509 email attribute in gridmanager. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2655\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2655'); return false;\" title=\"Bugs in gridmanager's handling of x509 email attribute\">#2655</a></span> Bad handling could lead to memory leaks, crashes, and x509UserProxyEmail not being set in jobs forwarded via Condor-C.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2011-Nov-22 16:44", "status": "resolved", "created": "2011-Nov-22 16:23", "fixed_version": "2011-Nov-22 16:23", "broken_version": "v070700", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "Grid", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "#1934", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}